1. When it comes to the technology you use in your virtual collaboration strategy:
Solution : B. The most important thing is that you have standardize modes of communication and technology that you use as a team

2. In addition to agreeing on which technology to use and when, what else might your communication strategy include?
Solution : A. Setting up rules for virtual meetings

3. Which type of virtual team includes people who work in the office, people who work out of the office, and people who occasionally work from other locations?
Solution : A. Hybrid virtual team

4. What is one thing you can do to create culture on your virtual team?
Solution : C. Give your virtual direct reports the opportunity to travel to the office for important events
